<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.3.8">
<l>alamu māḻip paṭaiyu muṭaiyār namakkaṉparāy</l>
<l>calama tākit takavoṉ ṟilarnān toḻutumeḻu</l>
<l>ulavu kālnal kaḻiyōṅ kutaṇpaim poḻilūṭicai</l>
<l>pulavu kāṉal kaḷivaṇ ṭiṉampā ṭupullāṇiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who bears the plough and the discus weapon, having been beloved to us,</l>
<l>[Now] behaving falsely, is without any decency.</l>
<l rend="indent">[Even so] arise; we will worship [him]</l>
<l>In Pullāṇi where swarms of intoxicated bees</l>
<l rend="indent">sing melodies on the reeking shore,</l>
<l>In the midst of tall, cool, green groves in the fine backwater</l>
<l rend="indent">with wandering breezes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
